批准萨布丽娜·卡彭特在教堂拍摄音乐录影带的牧师被解除“教牧监督”和额外职责https://www.nme.com/news/music/priest-who-approved-sabrina-carpenters-music-video-shoot-in-a-church-relieved-of-pastoral-oversight-and-additional-duties- 3814231?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=牧师批准了萨布丽娜木匠音乐视频在教堂拍摄，解除了教牧监督和额外职责Surej SinghWed, 20 Nov 2024 03:19:00 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3814231 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于他在“羽毛”音乐录影带中的角色以及其他“严重违规证据”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/priest-who-approved-sabrina-carpenters-music-video-shoot-in-a-church-relieved-of-pastoral-oversight-and-additional-duties-3814231">批准萨布丽娜·卡彭特在教堂拍摄音乐录影带的后牧师被解除了“教牧监督”和额外职责，该牧师</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2023 年批准<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特</a>在教堂拍摄《羽毛》音乐录影带的布鲁克林牧师已被解除职务。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sabrina-carpenter-short-n-sweet-review-3787293">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) – “Short n&#39; Sweet”评论：一位新的流行公主的崛起</a></strong></li></ul><p>去年10月，卡彭特发布了《Feather》的音乐录影带，视频中她在卡梅尔山圣母报喜教区（布鲁克林的一座罗马天主教堂）跳舞，并在棺材上写着“RIP bitch”。</p><p>视频发布后不久，许多宗教团体成员就视频中卡彭特在教堂里衣着暴露的行为表达了不满。不久之后，杰米·吉甘蒂洛主教被<a href="https://www.stereogum.com/2243800/catholic-priest-stripped-of-administrative-duties-for-allowing-sabrina-carpenter-video-shoot-in-brooklyn-church/news/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">解除了行政职务</a>。</p><p>在教堂 Facebook 页面上发布的<a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=743576697797239&amp;set=pb.100064347473050.-2207520000" target="_blank" rel="noopener">道歉声明</a>中，吉甘蒂洛表示，他批准这次拍摄是为了“进一步加强年轻创意艺术家之间的联系，这些艺术家是这个社区的很大一部分。”他后来说，他被告知该视频将包含葬礼场景，但最终结果“不是最初呈现给我的”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sabrina Carpenter - 羽毛（官方视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kLbn61Z4LDI?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>现在，据透露，由于最近发现了更多“严重违规行为”，吉甘蒂耶洛在教会的“任何牧师监督或治理角色”被进一步解除。</p><p>据<a href="https://apnews.com/article/sabrina-carpenter-music-video-church-controversy-52bcc40c18a934aa518be720b9c531dc" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>美联社报道</em></a>，主教罗伯特·布伦南 (Robert Brennan) 在一份声明中表示，吉甘蒂耶洛在对神父进行调查后被解除职务。据透露，吉甘蒂洛曾向纽约市前市长埃里克·亚当斯政府的一名前成员支付未经授权的款项，目前正在接受腐败调查。</p><p>布伦南说，视频曝光后，一项调查显示，吉甘蒂耶洛向纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯政府的一名前高级助手进行了未经授权的财务转账，该助手正在因腐败指控接受调查。</p><p>新的腐败指控，再加上萨布丽娜·卡彭特视频中他在社区中已经恶化的形象，导致教会任命维托尔德·姆罗齐耶夫斯基主教作为吉甘蒂耶洛的继任者。 </p><figure id="attachment_3808515" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3808515" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3808515" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/sabrina-carpenter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3808515" class="wp-caption-text">萨布丽娜·卡彭特。图片来源：Gilbert Flores/Billboard via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在卡彭特的其他新闻中，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-reveals-guests-for-her-netflix-holiday-special-3813911">最近透露了参加她即将推出的 Netflix 假日特别节目“胡言乱语的圣诞节”的嘉宾名单</a>。该特别节目将于 12 月 6 日首播，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查佩尔·罗恩</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tyla">泰拉</a>、昆塔·布伦森、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cara-delevingne">卡拉·迪瓦伊</a>、凯尔·穆尼、梅根·斯托尔特等人将出演。</p><p>上周，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/watch-sabrina-carpenter-bring-out-christina-aguilera-for-what-a-girl-wants-at-the-short-n-sweet-tour-3813311">在洛杉矶的一场演出中推出了《女孩想要什么》</a>中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christina-aguilera">克里斯蒂娜·阿奎莱拉</a>，并“逮捕”了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/bottoms-finally-lands-uk-release-date-3513027"><em>《Bottoms》的</em></a>女演员雷切尔·森诺特。 “你想进监狱吗？但是，以一种可爱的方式？” “朱诺号”开始前，卡彭特问道。 “我真的很慌张，因为我正在想象我们在一起的未来，”她说，然后递上了她的粉红色毛茸茸的手铐。</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">格莱美提名者</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-uk-and-european-tour-for-2025-buy-tickets-3776153">最近还宣布了她的巡演英国和欧洲站</a>，该巡演将于明年举行，前<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/rachel-chinouriri-15-01-2024-3570580"><em>NME</em>封面</a>明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rachel-chinouriri">Rachel Chinouriri</a>将作为特邀嘉宾。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-reveals-guests-for-her-netflix-holiday-special-3813911"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>演出将于 3 月 3 日在都柏林 3Arena 拉开帷幕，随后还将在伯明翰、伦敦和曼彻斯特举行演出 - 请参阅下面的所有日期并<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/sabrina-carpenter-tickets/artist/2001092?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wr6WK%3A2K9xyKR7zUPb3vE3Q-UkCUhdxsCzkYRk0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>抢票。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/priest-who-approved-sabrina-carpenters-music-video-shoot-in-a-church-relieved-of-pastoral-oversight-and-additional-duties-3814231">批准萨布丽娜·卡彭特在教堂拍摄音乐录影带的后牧师被解除了“教牧监督”和额外职责，该牧师</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
